executeBorrow(mapping(address => DataTyp.notice: Implements the borrow feature. Borrowing allows users that provided collateral to draw liquidity from the Aave protocol proportionally to their collateralization power. For isolated positions, it also increases the isolated debt.

executeRepay(mapping(address => DataType.notice: Implements the repay feature. Repaying transfers the underlying back to the aToken and clears the equivalent amount of debt for the user by burning the corresponding debt token. For isolated positions, it also reduces the isolated debt.
